Now I know from where the 125 pages limit comes from.
static int zone_balance_ratio[MAX_NR_ZONES] = { 32, 128, 128, };
16M/4k/32 = 125
Probably there is a mismatch between zone->free_pages and
free_pages.{min,low,high}
